				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I know this has been talked about for a while now but what is the general  fix people would like with it?
<br />

<br />
people have said our class doesnt get the fixes because we change our minds about everything. well lets try to agree on a fix here and see what happens?
<br />

<br />
Are biggest problem is that slow is a very powerful spell that kills all damage shields usefullness and takes our only group utility and throws it out the window. How do we fix it? 
<br />

<br />
two main ideas have been mentioned.
<br />

<br />
1. increase the damage output of the shield and by what number should it be.
<br />

<br />
2. add in a stun proc and how long/often should it proc.
<br />

<br />
which would you like to see happen?
<br />

<br />
I would like to see damage shields in general to have the power to place a class in balance with slow, meaning groups would have an option to either find a slower or find a damage shielding class.
<br />

<br />

<br />
as far as pvp balance. I dont think an increase/stun added would be over powerful. most classes can get dispelling items to get around a DS. 
<br />

<br />

<br />
so while sony is in a fixing mood < depending if we do see an improvement in pets <img src="images/smiles/icon_biggrin.gif" alt="Very Happy" border="0" /> > lets see if we can get this fixed like a part two to class balance  <img src="images/smiles/icon_biggrin.gif" alt="Very Happy" border="0" /><br />_________________<br />Pets need loving too....
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=424003" target="_blank" class="postlink">Gnuu</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
