				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">OK I think this is a great idea to help boost the usefulness of mages.  I think we should push this, with these two main factors.
<br />

<br />
1) DS is based on the amount of damage received by the tank (or whoever has the DS).  With a number of 75 when faced with slowed, high risk LDoN, and other similar mobs (like Vxed or first  sewer).
<br />

<br />
2) Increase the duration so our MGB is useful.  Seriously, MGB is almost a 9 point waste... at least make it with 20% duration buff it lasts for 50+ minutes.
<br />

<br />
Sound good?  Can people jump on board with this and try to get it pushed?  I just thought the only problematic thing would be maybe a fight like Fennin or any other hard hitting mob type encounters... but still this would give us a balance if you attributed that DPS to the mages.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
