<br />
(Would require additional codig so unlkely but I thought it was interesting)
<br />

<br />
Increase the top end damage of the DS but have the value increase over time.
<br />

<br />
DS would start at 50pt and increase to 300pt (for example) over a few seconds.  Fast hitting mobs would be hit for 50pt and slowed mobs would be hit for greater amounts depending on how much had been accumulated in the DS since the last hit.
<br />

<br />
Just thinking out loud.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
