			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">there is no way to balance a % ds unless you put a hardcap on it. 
<br />

<br />
a 1000 hitting mob slowed 50% slowed with a 25% ds 250 a hit at 2 seconds per hit = 125 dps. 
<br />

<br />
our current ds = 25 dps
<br />

<br />
a 1000 hitting mob unslowed = 250 dps 
<br />
 our current ds = 50dps
<br />

<br />
a 300 hitting mob unslowed = 75 dps 
<br />

<br />
a 300 hitting mob slowed = 37 dps
<br />

<br />
a 3000 hitting mob unslowd = 750 dps
<br />
a 3000 hitting mob slowed (elemental mini) = 370 dps. (or double our current TOTAL dps) 
<br />

<br />
drop it down to 10% 
<br />
and were still at 150 dps extra on a 50% slowed 3000 hitter 
<br />
and were at 15 dps extra on a 300 hitter or less than our existing ds. 
<br />

